{"tid":2003250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國針對中国人「仇恨犯罪」急升","createTime":"2020-05-05T16:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T03:10:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"55fc29d4586dd2f1aa9187b293993d453f8b6359","tid":2003250,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T16:19:10.000Z","msg":"英國傳媒報道，新型肺炎疫情爆發，針對中國人的「仇恨犯罪」急升。<br />\n<br />\n警方數字顯示，今年一至三月收到至少267宗針對當地中國人受騷擾的報案，包括毆打、搶劫、騷擾和刑事毀壞，數目是之前兩年的近三倍。<br />\n<br />\n受害者形容他們被人揮拳、當面吐痰、咳嗽和出言侮辱。<br />\n<br />\n一名護士學生說，受到醫院病人和同事歧視，有同事叫他帶同病毒返回中國。他說感到無助，不知可以向誰傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n亦有自小由香港移民到英國的人說，試過在倫敦街頭被一個女子用粗言責罵。<br />\n<br />\n全國專門處理仇恨犯罪的警官說，無人需要為疫情負責，每個人都有權免受騷擾。當局會以非常認真的態度處理案件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524428-20200505.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524428-20200505.htm&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=7ad2dced\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1524428-20200505.htm&h=1281a04a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1524428-20200505.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0b44852a18ba1beb4a91dbf9e7b0348ac9fda9d5","tid":2003250,"uid":116021,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T16:20:59.000Z","msg":"着Hong Kong is Not China tee出街會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a928fee98a1d2d5c136197e1e568ca33b606ed6c","tid":2003250,"uid":325718,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"0b44852a18ba1beb4a91dbf9e7b0348ac9fda9d5","tid":2003250,"uid":116021,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T16:20:59.000Z","msg":"着Hong Kong is Not China tee出街會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"班支那人咪跟住著，之後香港人繼續俾人當支那<br />\n你見訪問特朗普嗰兩隻支那幾冇骨氣就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\